---
title: Skillet Chicken Pot Pie with Homemade Biscuits and Thyme Gravy
description: Traditional chicken pot pie is a labor of love—this comfort food favorite is usually an all-day affair. Luckily, we have a time-saving secret! 3-ingredient cream biscuits are just as tender and satisfying as pastry crust, but take a fraction of the time. Baked over a creamy and luxurious filling, it’s just as good as Grandma’s.
